{'-25': 1, '45': 1, 'Katelyn initially saw 50 fairies. One of her friends saw half as many, so they saw 50 / 2 = 25 fairies. These 25 fairies joined the initial 50 fairies that Katelyn had seen, making it 25 + 50 = 75 fairies. 

Ten minutes later, 30 fairies flew away, leaving 75 - 30 = 45 fairies.

So, the number of fairies remaining after ten minutes is 45.': 1}

